      "role": "user",
      "content": "i spent twenty years building a theory that everyone thought was groundbreaking. turns out i was just wrong. or worse, i was just delusional. everything i wrote, every lecture, every paper... it's all just a monument to a lie. i don't even know who i am without the work. there is literally nothing left.",
